{"tid":1623684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［Water Revolution] 水魔法 消防喉","createTime":"2019-10-05T01:01:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T16:54:20.000Z","uid":186,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4e6510384c70dc3f281498b8ae0c1aa6569d88dc","tid":1623684,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:01:05.000Z","msg":"香港有完善消防條例，防火意思高<br />\n所有商場街道必須有，洗手間都有<br />\n<br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好用水魔法</span></span></div></strong><strong><br />\n雖然殺傷平民力低<br />\n雖然依家得縱火 無縱水罪<br />\n雖然畫面睇落相比放火和平</strong><br />\n<strong><br />\n但所有機器人怕水<br />\n同埋狗啊人啊在水面 行動力減慢<br />\n成個詢問處水浸 點搞啊<br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n強烈譴責以下情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n扶手電梯 入閘機 ATM係機器<br />\n有水淋完好危險<br />\n玻璃加水 點行啊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eJU17sV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeJU17sV.jpg&h=476687c1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JYFwLeB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJYFwLeB.jpg&h=b9a2171e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QE917s0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQE917s0.jpg&h=e9b011ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FWXK5eJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFWXK5eJ.jpg&h=7751d85d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kdDY9Gp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkdDY9Gp.jpg&h=eac28956&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"766a2e6fe4b342e92c0dc549377652e4271d9a81","tid":1623684,"uid":186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T01:01:28.000Z","msg":"成地濕哂 勁危險囉<img src=\"/assets/fa